snippet.title: Blasphemous: Strife and Ruin - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Miriam from Bloodstained: Ritual of the Night is summoned to Cvstodia in the upcoming free update for Blasphemous, available on February 18, 2021.

Additionally, the update will feature a Boss Rush Mode, new challenge rooms, new Render Modes, and more.

#IGN #Blashpemous
